    "causal_summary": "The memory index must stay correct without operator intervention: new and changed spec docs need indexing, orphaned rows need sweeping, and packet renames/moves need reconciliation, all without flooding writers or stalling the daemon. The same index database also needs a durable rollback net so a corrupt or oversized state can be recovered.",
